					<h1 itemprop="name">Why Jill Abramson Was Fired</h1>

					<h3>By <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><a href="http://www.newyorker.com/contributors/ken-auletta" title="Ken Auletta" rel="author" itemprop="name author">Ken Auletta</a></span></h3>
					<!-- TODO: Add LinkedIn and Pinterest Support [#98] -->



